  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mountain Legends 5 is our car racing title of the Mountain Legends Series for your Apple Mac & Microsoft Windows devices. Race to the finish line before it’s too late. Defeat your opponents & be the first to cross the finish line. This Game Works with Keyboard/Gamepad/Touch Screen Devices as well.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8 different vehicles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Good Quality of Graphics.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >14 different environments.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Formula Car Racing.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All the levels are unlocked.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Watch AI Play.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All the cars are unlocked.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No Ads & In App Purchases.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Totally offline game.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keyboard Layout:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Button A: Left</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Button B: Look Back</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Button C: Change Camera</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Button D: Right</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Button E: Right Indicator Light</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Button F: Boost/Nitro</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Button G: Slow Motion</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Button H: Horn</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Button I: Engine On/Off</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Button K: Head Light High Beam</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Button L: Head Light Low Beam</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Button M: Options/Menu</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Button P: Pause/Resume</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Button Q: Left Indicator Light</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Button S: Back/Brake/Backward</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Button W: Forward</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Button Space: Handbrake</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Button Shift: Gear Shift Up (Manual Gear Only)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Button Control: Gear Shift Down (Manual Gear Only)</p>",
